Describe how you would thoroughly test the "www.freshly.com/login" page below:


- For the email and password fields, various injections including cross-site scripting and SQL
- Verify error messages for blank and malformed email addresses
- Verify message for entering an email addresses that already exists in the system
- Verify error messages for entering no password or the wrong password
- Verify that the 'Forgot Password?' flow works correctly
- Verify that the 'Get Started' link directs to freshly.com/join-now
- Verify that all the links on the page have the correct hrefs
- Verify look and functionality of page on Chrome, Firefox and Edge
- And, of course, valid email-password combos can successfully log in